title: Fold Your Own Zombie! 2011 Calendar
features: With the Fold Your Own Zombie 2013 Wall Calendar gleefully gruesome zombies come alive as you create a year's worth of monsters. Punch out the pieces of paper corpses entombed in a handy pocket at the back of the calendar, then fold them into gloriously gory walking-dead models.* Create twelve detailed 3-D zombie models from paper punch-outs.* Original artwork and designs.* Appeals to all ages!
description: Accord Publishing is a Denver based publisher of fun and interactive children's books.
